{"tid":648399,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★5月3-4日 HSI drop 10000pt?]中美貿易戰：傳中方將以「強硬立場」談判","createTime":"2018-04-30T15:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T16:02:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63c1ed5012518f18e4b67b78d7867365c06fa296","tid":648399,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"中美雙方已落實，將於周四(5月3日)及周五(5月4日)在中國會面，談及貿易問題。<br />\n<br />\n外國傳媒報道，有熟悉中國政策人士表示，中方不會在談判中討論美方兩大要求：強制中國削減1,000億美元貿易逆差；遏制中國3,000億美元用於產業升級的計劃，例如人工智能、半導體、電動車，以及商用飛機等先進技術。原因在於中方認為，中國經濟已足夠大並有足夠彈性，有足夠能力能站起來面對美國。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，中國政府在周一(4月30日)完成了歷時3天的高層會談，並邀請了一些外國人士，以確保中方的立場能傳到海外。故此，沒有人能估計周四及周五會發生甚麼事，能否達成協議是未知數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180430/bkn-20180430220758870-0430_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180430%2Fbkn-20180430220758870-0430_00842_001.html&d=SoHoN3jx8HdMuib1ab2rs5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=91f17ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180430/bkn-20180430220758870-0430_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6cf918515286946daed4399bcc0f4099100d52d4","tid":648399,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"drop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dbf650a46f53748571680751a24763c3aada39","tid":648399,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"贏＝sing"},{"pid":"a8896241847f9e6c65c0fba5335ad6bf16f338ac","tid":648399,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6cf918515286946daed4399bcc0f4099100d52d4","tid":648399,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"drop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:02:08.000Z","msg":"咪登啦<br />\n成手淡倉<br />\n<br />\n科研或贏<im